text:
Sooo happy to find new vegetarian stall near my office!
Plus have wide variety of menu everyday instead of just economic rice.
Will come here often

When they just open, I tried and aunty was quite friendly and portion was just right. Wanted to review but 1 month + forward now I try again… the ingredients was lesser and $4.50 not worth anymore. I guess no more next time.
Only 1 person at stall handling everything when we visit.. need more help
Branch of the original in Fajah. Excellent as ever. Tried the vegetarian chicken rice & veg fish ball mee. Both were excellent! Highly recommended and it’s closer to home for me.
Petai Sambal Fried rice for $6. 50,  for chilli lovers.
